    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1902-06-27T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1902-06-27T00:00:00-05:00" n="553"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d553">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Raikes</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">British Embassy</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1902-06-27">
                            <hi rend="italic">June 27, 1902</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 165.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I have the honor to inform you that I have
                    received a dispatch from the Marquis of Lansdowne stating that the United States
                    consul <pb facs="0618" n="538" xml:id="pg_538"/> at Guadeloupe, who is now at
                    Martinique, has undertaken the protection of British interests at that place in
                    the absence of any representative of His Majesty’s Government.</p>
                <p>I have the honor, by direction of the Marquis of Lansdowne, to express to your
                    Government the cordial thanks of His Majesty’s Government for this friendly
                    action, and to request that you will be so good as to convey them to the United
                    States consul at Martinique.</p>
                <p>I have, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Arthur S. Raikes.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
